0:02:23.743,0:02:25.260
What is going on?

0:02:25.260,0:02:26.846
You should be ashamed to ask.

0:02:26.846,0:02:28.890
The woman your sister sent here

0:02:28.890,0:02:31.080
committed an utterly shameless act.

0:02:31.190,0:02:33.560
Is she truly the shameless one?

0:02:33.610,0:02:36.800
After all, it was not Noble Lady Lustré
who wrote this letter.

0:02:37.097,0:02:38.650
What letter?

0:02:38.650,0:02:40.150
This is what happened.

0:02:40.160,0:02:42.556
Last night, I asked Ruyi to bring some snacks
from the Imperial Kitchen.

0:02:42.820,0:02:45.520
She happened to see Xiao-Lezi, 
the Third Prince's servant.

0:02:45.680,0:02:47.345
He was lurking around Long Street.

0:02:47.360,0:02:49.158
The Third Prince has always been prudent.

0:02:49.460,0:02:50.870
He's not that kind of person.

0:02:50.870,0:02:52.420
He's been prudent?

0:02:52.420,0:02:54.500
I'm afraid that's just a façade.

0:02:54.840,0:02:57.760
Your Majesty, please forgive my bluntness.

0:02:57.949,0:03:00.540
But you haven't educated your son well.

0:03:00.540,0:03:03.040
The Third Prince is young and lacks worldly wisdom.

0:03:03.430,0:03:05.600
This worthless wretch must have seduced him.

0:03:05.680,0:03:08.835
Your Majesty, I did not...  I did not!

0:03:08.835,0:03:10.761
She was selected by Noble Prince Guo's estate.

0:03:11.251,0:03:13.328
No good can come from a lowly maid.

0:03:14.310,0:03:18.480
I believe that the Third Prince is innocent here 
and has been framed.

0:03:18.614,0:03:20.480
But the messenger was caught red-handed.

0:03:20.570,0:03:22.400
The Third Prince wrote this letter himself!

0:03:22.450,0:03:24.120
This wretch must have first seduced him!

0:03:24.249,0:03:26.080
- But...
- Enough, stop arguing.

0:03:26.120,0:03:27.240
Your Majesty!

0:03:27.240,0:03:29.280
You cannot let your own son suffer such injustice!

0:03:30.290,0:03:33.600
Your Majesty, I truly didn't seduce the Third Prince!

0:03:33.760,0:03:36.245
You acted improperly and seduced an imperial prince.

0:03:36.962,0:03:38.880
I now grant you a way to end your own life.

0:03:38.880,0:03:41.120
Your Majesty, I didn't do it!

0:03:41.670,0:03:45.420
You have told me your whole story, 
and I don't want to hear any more of it.

0:03:45.760,0:03:48.080
- Su Peisheng.
- Your Majesty.

0:03:48.180,0:03:50.040
Take her out and bestow her a length of white silk.

0:03:50.100,0:03:51.080
Yes.

0:03:51.230,0:03:53.640
- Your Majesty!
- You two, come here!

0:03:53.640,0:03:55.380
Your Majesty! Your Majesty!

0:03:55.810,0:03:57.020
I'm not guilty!

0:03:57.020,0:03:58.600
Your Majesty!

0:03:58.680,0:03:59.160
Your Majesty.

0:03:59.160,0:04:00.060
Enough!

0:04:00.060,0:04:02.123
I'm not guilty!

0:04:05.870,0:04:08.880
Hongshi has been kneeling since late last night
in Fengxian Hall [for Ancestor Worship].

0:04:09.370,0:04:11.320
This matter ends here.

0:04:12.000,0:04:15.200
I don't want to hear a word 
of gossip in the palace.

0:04:15.420,0:04:16.920
Yes.

0:04:16.920,0:04:18.540
You two are dismissed.

0:04:18.540,0:04:20.884
I have a question for Noble Consort Lumière.

0:04:23.010,0:04:24.727
 I bid Your Majesty goodbye.

0:04:30.140,0:04:34.440
Did Lord Consort Yu select Noble Lady Lustré?

0:04:34.600,0:04:35.730
Yes.

0:04:35.730,0:04:37.770
Is it possible that...

0:04:37.770,0:04:40.960
someone arranged for Noble Lady Lustré
to seduce an imperial prince,

0:04:41.040,0:04:42.320
in order to usurp my throne?

0:04:42.320,0:04:45.030
Your Majesty, why do you ask?

0:04:47.654,0:04:49.402
Hongshi is my eldest son.

0:04:50.370,0:04:54.426
The court is hotly debating whether to name 
him or a younger prince as the Crown Prince.

0:04:55.210,0:04:57.250
Destroying Hongshi's reputation

0:04:57.250,0:04:59.255
is the same as destroying mine.

0:05:01.380,0:05:04.465
Your Majesty, Yuyin would absolutely never dare to do that.

0:05:05.930,0:05:08.800
She would not, but what about
Noble Prince Guo?

0:05:08.960,0:05:10.550
I can vouch for him, too.

0:05:10.550,0:05:12.481
On what grounds do you vouch for him?

0:05:13.215,0:05:15.096
Everyone in this palace

0:05:16.140,0:05:20.236
experienced the chaos of the nine lords' 
battle for the throne

0:05:20.820,0:05:24.640
and how terrifying the princes' lust 
for the throne was.

0:05:25.990,0:05:30.640
Noble Prince Guo was one of the prior emperor's 
preferred choices for Crown Prince.

0:05:32.540,0:05:35.600
Your Majesty is wise.  
But Noble Prince Guo truly would not dare.

0:05:35.700,0:05:37.870
My concern is that

0:05:37.870,0:05:40.000
although he dares not do anything to me,

0:05:40.250,0:05:42.775
he could be using Lord Consort Yu's hands

0:05:43.341,0:05:45.526
to scheme against my sons.

0:05:45.703,0:05:49.584
All these years, Noble Prince Guo's heart has been
loyal and devoted to Your Majesty.

0:05:49.584,0:05:50.963
Loyal and devoted?

0:05:52.140,0:05:54.777
Who can gouge out his heart and prove that?

0:05:59.140,0:06:06.560
So, even though you and Noble Consort Estime
feel that I have wrongly convicted Noble Lady Lustré,

0:06:06.760,0:06:09.019
I have to protect the reputation of the imperial family.

0:06:09.396,0:06:11.320
I must protect my son.

0:06:11.410,0:06:14.000
I can't expose myself 
to any potential manipulation.

0:06:14.030,0:06:15.247
Your Majesty,

0:06:15.700,0:06:18.721
Noble Lady Lustré has truly suffered injustice.

0:06:18.910,0:06:20.460
It was done for the Great Qing,

0:06:20.460,0:06:23.200
therefore it was not an injustice to have wronged her.

0:06:24.380,0:06:26.797
Since Yuyin is your honorary sister,

0:06:28.170,0:06:30.240
suspicion must be averted from you.

0:06:31.140,0:06:34.180
There have been so many trivial matters 
in the palace lately.

0:06:34.180,0:06:35.660
Perhaps you're tired.

0:06:36.810,0:06:39.520
The Empress will take care of the palace affairs

0:06:39.520,0:06:41.637
and Noble Consort Estime will assist her.

0:06:41.980,0:06:44.243
Is Your Majesty...

0:06:45.912,0:06:47.662
suspicious of me?

0:06:47.680,0:06:49.341
The Empress is right.

0:06:50.200,0:06:52.450
As the mother of an imperial prince,

0:06:52.450,0:06:55.135
you cannot escape suspicion.

0:07:29.150,0:07:30.935
Imperial Father.

0:07:48.170,0:07:50.307
Two slaps:

0:07:50.760,0:07:55.022
One for coveting your Imperial Father's woman,

0:07:55.550,0:07:59.154
The other for coveting the Emperor's woman.

0:08:00.470,0:08:01.850
Imperial Father!

0:08:01.850,0:08:02.923
This is all my fault.

0:08:03.480,0:08:04.711
I beg for your forgiveness.

0:08:05.480,0:08:07.015
Of course I will forgive you.

0:08:07.690,0:08:10.178
Not only because you're my eldest son,

0:08:10.480,0:08:12.480
but also a son of the Aisin-Gioro Clan.

0:08:12.820,0:08:15.160
The prestige of the imperial family must be protected.

0:08:15.320,0:08:17.570
Yes, I admit my fault.

0:08:17.570,0:08:19.280
You admit your fault.

0:08:19.330,0:08:21.780
But someone else has shouldered the blame for you.

0:08:22.580,0:08:24.800
I have already executed Noble Lady Lustré.

0:08:26.790,0:08:28.750
She... she...

0:08:28.750,0:08:30.670
Of course she was innocent.

0:08:30.670,0:08:32.425
You're the one to blame.

0:08:32.840,0:08:34.472
But you are my son,

0:08:35.470,0:08:40.000
and I can't expose you to harm 
just because of a woman.

0:08:41.784,0:08:44.230
I caused her death!

0:08:44.230,0:08:45.600
Yes.

0:08:45.600,0:08:47.160
You caused her death!

0:08:47.650,0:08:49.270
You forgot "the bounds of Heaven and Earth"

0:08:49.270,0:08:51.070
and "the moral ethics of human beings."

0:08:51.070,0:08:52.860
Imperial Father...

0:08:52.860,0:08:55.283
Stay here and reflect deeply on your wrongdoings.

0:08:56.860,0:08:58.800
If you make another mistake,

0:08:58.910,0:09:01.000
even I will not be able to save you.

0:09:22.100,0:09:23.553
Lumière.

0:09:25.430,0:09:27.065
It's so quiet here.

0:09:27.480,0:09:29.613
You can even hear the flowers falling.

0:09:31.020,0:09:34.880
Your palace is hardly ever this quiet.

0:09:36.780,0:09:39.070
No one in the palace is favored forever.

0:09:40.570,0:09:42.575
Once you realize this, there is nothing to fear.

0:09:43.330,0:09:44.740
Losing favor -

0:09:45.080,0:09:47.160
If you treat it as a torment,

0:09:47.160,0:09:49.330
then your life will be a torment.

0:09:49.330,0:09:50.580
If you face it calmly,

0:09:50.580,0:09:52.670
then your life will be calm.

0:09:53.960,0:09:57.600
Nothing matters but one's own state of mind.

0:09:59.338,0:10:01.329
When you get a chance, Estime,

0:10:01.329,0:10:03.645
could you offer incense to Noble Lady Lustré with me?

0:10:04.060,0:10:05.520
She is a pitiful soul.

0:10:05.520,0:10:06.822
All right.

0:10:07.350,0:10:09.060
It was all my fault.

0:10:09.060,0:10:11.652
My intention was to limit the Empress's power.

0:10:12.381,0:10:14.374
But I pushed too hard

0:10:15.015,0:10:17.181
and blame fell upon you and Noble Lady Lustré instead.

0:10:17.584,0:10:19.774
Noble Lady Lustré indeed suffered injustice.

0:10:20.000,0:10:24.345
Yet Noble Prince Guo was cast under 
undue suspicion: a far greater injustice.

0:10:24.571,0:10:26.320
I never expected this.

0:10:26.410,0:10:28.450
His Majesty has never liked the Third Prince.

0:10:29.410,0:10:31.875
Yet he has protected him throughout this affair.

0:10:32.290,0:10:34.744
He showed a heavy hand in executing Noble Lady Lustré,

0:10:35.250,0:10:37.614
which has given the Empress a chance to bite back

0:10:37.840,0:10:39.340
and gain the upper hand.

0:10:39.340,0:10:43.308
His Majesty values prestige, so he always considers the good name of the imperial family.

0:10:44.100,0:10:46.350
No matter how much an heir misbehaves,

0:10:46.350,0:10:48.200
he is still the Emperor's son.

0:10:48.270,0:10:51.800
And in this instance, the designation of 
the Crown Prince is also at stake.

0:10:51.980,0:10:54.463
Naturally, His Majesty is more cautious.

0:10:56.320,0:10:58.650
I made some of your favorite desserts.

0:10:59.427,0:11:01.832
I don't have much of an appetite.

0:11:03.200,0:11:04.730
What's the matter?

0:11:04.730,0:11:07.018
Perhaps I've had too many these days.

0:11:08.410,0:11:10.450
Jinxi, prepare a bowl of sour plum soup.

0:11:10.450,0:11:11.361
Yes.

0:11:12.266,0:11:14.340
You don't usually like sour food.

0:11:16.833,0:11:20.399
It's been a while.
I'm rather craving it now.

0:11:21.470,0:11:23.764
A good appetite is a blessing in itself.

0:11:25.280,0:11:26.163
Oh...

0:11:27.182,0:11:28.380
Lumière,

0:11:29.280,0:11:31.438
are you again...?

0:11:33.020,0:11:36.236
Ah, what wonderful blessings you have!

0:11:36.236,0:11:37.690
With this baby,

0:11:37.690,0:11:40.734
all our current difficulties will be resolved.

0:11:41.570,0:11:43.221
I will go inform His Majesty immediately.

0:11:43.410,0:11:45.990
This soothes my remorse over implicating you.

0:11:47.457,0:11:49.437
My difficulties aren't hard to resolve.

0:11:50.290,0:11:53.750
But I'm worried about Noble Prince Guo and Yuyin.

0:11:56.584,0:11:58.487
How has Noble Consort Lumière been these days?

0:11:59.550,0:12:03.953
The doctors say that Her Highness has been languid
due to disharmony between Spleen and Stomach.

0:12:05.220,0:12:08.680
Her Highness has been feeling aggrieved recently.
She's not to blame.

0:12:09.260,0:12:11.078
She's not?

0:12:11.770,0:12:13.161
So I am to blame?

0:12:13.350,0:12:14.589
I would not dare, Your Majesty.

0:12:16.270,0:12:19.515
I had my reasons for asking her those questions.

0:12:20.570,0:12:22.030
This morning,

0:12:22.860,0:12:24.985
Ortai and Maci had a heated debate.

0:12:25.740,0:12:29.272
Back and forth... still about
the designation of the Crown Prince.

0:12:29.830,0:12:31.922
Whether inside or outside the palace,

0:12:32.450,0:12:34.611
who knows how many people are

0:12:35.040,0:12:37.865
eyeing my Dragon Throne.

0:12:39.090,0:12:42.330
Announcing my chosen Crown Prince is sure to cause
"a tumult of chickens and dogs."

0:12:43.812,0:12:47.176
I should come up with a plan lest things go wrong.

0:12:47.591,0:12:49.178
Your Majesty is wise.

0:12:49.760,0:12:52.430
Noble Consort Lumière is now with child.

0:12:55.222,0:12:57.711
I do not wish to see her distressed.

0:12:57.711,0:12:59.511
It is strange

0:12:59.511,0:13:04.472
that all of the recent events have been targeting Noble Consort Lumière.

0:13:05.240,0:13:07.200
It is rather suspicious.

0:13:07.200,0:13:08.704
Not that I'm unaware.

0:13:11.030,0:13:12.560
The harem

0:13:14.296,0:13:17.049
seems tranquil on the surface

0:13:17.615,0:13:19.511
but murky waters lie beneath.

0:13:20.341,0:13:22.400
I intend to purify the waters.

0:13:22.670,0:13:24.090
But once you touch the bottom,

0:13:24.090,0:13:27.251
it is mostly women's concerns, unworthy of my time.

0:13:27.930,0:13:31.760
Empress Première's devotion to her sister has led me

0:13:33.720,0:13:36.021
to turn a blind eye in many situations

0:13:36.021,0:13:37.440
and the events pass.

0:13:38.730,0:13:43.183
In sum, trouble within the harem is nothing.

0:13:43.900,0:13:45.530
What I'm more concerned about

0:13:46.360,0:13:49.743
is collusion between the court and the harem

0:13:50.858,0:13:53.404
to plot against me.

0:13:54.233,0:13:56.733
I have no choice but to be wary.

0:13:59.210,0:14:00.480
Your Majesty is sage.

0:14:01.380,0:14:04.762
Deliver my desserts to the Palace of Eternal Longevity.

0:14:05.510,0:14:08.180
Let Noble Consort Lumière know 
that I am thinking of her.

0:14:08.180,0:14:09.880
Yes. I will go right away.

