0:14:59.230,0:15:01.730
Today is the fifteenth day of the month - 
a grand occasion.

0:15:01.730,0:15:04.110
With His Majesty's incense offering,

0:15:04.110,0:15:07.297
our Great Qing will be peaceful and prosperous.

0:15:13.234,0:15:16.709
I haven't held the Sixth Prince for quite a while.

0:15:20.460,0:15:22.540
He's gained some weight.

0:15:22.540,0:15:24.332
The Sixth Prince has grown taller again.

0:15:24.710,0:15:26.290
Because of Your Majesty's care,

0:15:26.290,0:15:29.410
he wants to grow taller and stronger for Your Majesty.

0:15:29.712,0:15:32.108
I care for the princes and the princesses,

0:15:32.760,0:15:34.857
and of course I care for all of you.

0:15:36.390,0:15:38.130
The days are getting hotter.

0:15:39.310,0:15:41.220
Don't seek relief by eating raw or cold foods.

0:15:42.020,0:15:43.850
Don't stand in a draught when you're sweating.

0:15:43.850,0:15:46.560
I thank Your Majesty for your caring words.

0:15:46.610,0:15:49.440
I heard Noble Consort Lumière coughing when getting up this morning.

0:15:50.650,0:15:52.671
It made my mind ill at ease.

0:15:54.110,0:15:56.061
Noble Consort Lumière has always exerted herself.

0:15:56.740,0:15:58.876
If you cannot be helpful,

0:15:59.253,0:16:01.750
and instead cause her even a shred of worry,

0:16:01.750,0:16:04.490
that will upset me even more.

0:16:05.710,0:16:06.950
Yes.

0:16:07.710,0:16:10.200
There are a large number of servants in the harem.

0:16:11.130,0:16:12.854
Inevitably, that leads to gossip.

0:16:15.220,0:16:16.963
Starting with your own palace,

0:16:17.642,0:16:22.008
expel maids who come from the Han and Mongolian banners.

0:16:22.989,0:16:25.920
The maids from the Manchu banners 
will take turns serving.

0:16:26.900,0:16:28.020
Yes.

0:16:28.020,0:16:31.140
Nevertheless, Your Majesty's close servants 
should not be expelled.

0:16:32.650,0:16:35.261
I loathe servants who gossip.

0:16:37.490,0:16:41.990
First expel those who like to cause trouble
 behind others' backs.

0:16:44.573,0:16:49.633
The Dzungars are now a rising threat on the borders.

0:16:50.840,0:16:53.564
Cutting spending within the palace, even small amounts,

0:16:54.130,0:16:57.120
demonstrates our support for the front lines.

0:16:58.680,0:17:02.314
You should all act appropriately.

0:17:04.140,0:17:07.148
I will obey Your Majesty's instructions.

0:17:09.743,0:17:11.910
- I want this.
- This one should be here.

0:17:12.684,0:17:14.490
Putting it here is better.

0:17:14.490,0:17:17.384
I heard servants are being expelled from all over the palace.

0:17:17.610,0:17:21.314
This is how His Majesty expresses his 
displeasure with the Empress.

0:17:21.540,0:17:23.856
His Majesty's mind is unfathomable.

0:17:24.045,0:17:26.210
It's getting warmer.

0:17:26.210,0:17:28.554
I've noticed that you've been more reluctant to walk around.

0:17:29.170,0:17:32.160
 Every day you seem fatigued and lethargic.

0:17:32.250,0:17:34.510
This pregnancy is a bit strange.

0:17:34.510,0:17:39.000
I'm prone to feeling nauseous, and my chest feels heavy and tight.

