0:34:02.906,0:34:04.542
Peace to Your Majesty.

0:34:08.863,0:34:10.880
I have been busy with state affairs.

0:34:10.880,0:34:13.240
You look even more gaunt
than when I saw you two days ago.

0:34:14.800,0:34:19.120
It's all because of this naughty child in my belly.

0:34:20.090,0:34:21.720
Your Majesty didn't know

0:34:21.720,0:34:24.960
how he was tossing around in my belly all night.

0:34:25.470,0:34:26.930
I didn't sleep well.

0:34:26.930,0:34:29.084
This child is so active and playful,

0:34:29.310,0:34:31.550
he must be a healthy prince.

0:34:32.690,0:34:34.724
In the future, let me know if you can't sleep.

0:34:34.724,0:34:36.536
You'll have my company.

0:34:36.990,0:34:38.396
Your Majesty is busy with state affairs,

0:34:38.396,0:34:39.650
I dare not disturb your sleep.

0:34:39.650,0:34:41.573
The imperial heir is also a state affair.

0:34:41.950,0:34:44.503
I want you both to be safe and sound.

0:34:46.750,0:34:49.360
I have something to discuss with you.

0:34:50.866,0:34:51.720
What is it?

0:34:52.080,0:34:53.455
For the prior emperor's birth anniversary,

0:34:53.920,0:34:57.040
I want to send a prince to perform
the ceremony on my behalf.

0:34:57.550,0:34:59.342
Who do you think is most suitable?

0:35:00.130,0:35:01.696
In terms of both age and status,

0:35:02.300,0:35:04.399
the Third Prince is the most suitable candidate.

0:35:04.890,0:35:07.856
I certainly know that Hongshi is the most appropriate one.

0:35:08.850,0:35:12.800
He was my only son before Hongli and Hongyan were born.

0:35:13.650,0:35:15.494
Naturally I had high expectations of him.

0:35:15.860,0:35:19.350
However, the boy is obtuse and faint-hearted,

0:35:20.200,0:35:22.880
and has even been associating with officials privately.

0:35:23.370,0:35:24.950
During the final years of the prior emperor's reign,

0:35:24.950,0:35:26.740
there was great chaos

0:35:26.740,0:35:29.080
because many princes associated with officials

0:35:29.080,0:35:30.910
and plotted to usurp the throne.

0:35:31.460,0:35:33.320
How could he be so reckless?

0:35:35.000,0:35:36.550
The Third Prince is still young.

0:35:36.550,0:35:38.587
Naturally he cannot thoroughly consider his actions.

0:35:38.800,0:35:40.510
Your Majesty can simply point it out to him.

0:35:40.510,0:35:43.090
Even if I instruct him,

0:35:43.680,0:35:47.040
he already has his heart set on the throne.

0:35:48.020,0:35:50.260
Just like Yunsi, the former Eighth Prince.

0:35:51.140,0:35:54.497
No matter how our Imperial Father
advised or reprimanded the Eighth Prince,

0:35:55.310,0:35:56.896
it was futile.

0:35:56.896,0:35:58.720
The Third Prince is not like that.

0:35:59.453,0:36:01.906
He is the eldest among the princes.

0:36:02.530,0:36:05.007
It is inevitable that he thinks of himself 
as my successor.

0:36:05.620,0:36:07.530
All right, I've thought it through.

0:36:08.370,0:36:10.780
You just take care of your health.

0:36:12.540,0:36:15.780
A giant coral has arrived in tribute from Qiongzhou Province.

0:36:16.340,0:36:17.663
It is very rare.

0:36:18.210,0:36:21.830
Tibetan Buddhism sees red coral
as an embodiment of the Tathāgata Buddha.

0:36:22.260,0:36:24.370
I think it will bring peace to your pregnancy.

0:36:25.890,0:36:27.352
If it is truly such a marvellous coral,

0:36:28.140,0:36:30.472
it would be a pity if I am the only one to admire it.

0:36:31.480,0:36:34.560
Why don't I invite all the concubines
to the Palace of Eternal Longevity

0:36:34.560,0:36:36.364
to appreciate it together?

0:36:37.190,0:36:38.654
If you like.

0:36:39.396,0:36:40.568
It's good timing.

0:36:40.940,0:36:42.440
The priests at Baohua Hall

0:36:42.440,0:36:45.040
made some talismans for my baby.

0:36:45.740,0:36:48.830
They said that these talismans will be effective

0:36:48.830,0:36:51.450
if people of the highest status in the harem

0:36:51.450,0:36:53.330
place them in the lucky sachets

0:36:53.330,0:36:54.910
and fasten them to my bed.

0:36:55.210,0:36:57.880
I think the most appropriate people, of course,

0:36:57.880,0:37:01.240
are the Empress, the Imperial Noble Consort, 
and Noble Consort Estime.

0:37:01.670,0:37:03.500
And I will tie one myself.

0:37:03.500,0:37:05.080
That covers the four corners of the bed.

0:37:05.550,0:37:07.390
This will accumulate Heaven's blessings.

0:37:07.390,0:37:08.630
They surely will not refuse.

0:37:09.300,0:37:11.220
Her Majesty doesn't go out nowadays,

0:37:11.220,0:37:12.930
and has turned down many invitations.

0:37:13.730,0:37:15.354
But if Her Majesty doesn't come,

0:37:15.600,0:37:17.692
Heaven's blessing will be incomplete.

0:37:18.560,0:37:21.350
I will invite them, if you'd like that.

0:37:24.634,0:37:27.020
Why is the Empress still not here?

0:37:27.020,0:37:28.240
Your Majesty,

0:37:28.780,0:37:30.990
Her Majesty has already sent someone over,

0:37:31.410,0:37:33.620
saying that Her Majesty is not feeling well

0:37:33.620,0:37:35.042
and may not come today.

0:37:35.460,0:37:38.040
Why does she feel unwell when I invite her?

0:37:38.960,0:37:40.840
Maybe there's someone she doesn't want to see

0:37:40.840,0:37:42.450
in the Palace of Eternal Longevity.

0:37:43.170,0:37:45.380
So she feels unwell whenever she comes.

0:37:47.590,0:37:48.590
Su Peisheng.

0:37:48.590,0:37:49.550
Your Majesty.

0:37:49.550,0:37:51.290
Go invite the Empress yourself.

0:37:51.680,0:37:52.882
She is the head of the harem -

0:37:52.882,0:37:54.684
it's inappropriate for her to be absent.

0:37:55.100,0:37:56.437
Yes.

0:37:58.150,0:38:01.260
Look, this red coral is dark red but translucent.

0:38:01.570,0:38:02.782
It is such a rarity.

0:38:03.230,0:38:05.770
Noble Consort Lumière is in great favor indeed.

0:38:06.320,0:38:08.230
Your Majesty is very considerate.

0:38:08.910,0:38:12.360
This coral is even more radiant at night.

0:38:13.080,0:38:16.320
This coral is rare, but the Heavenly thoughtfulness is rarer.

0:38:16.790,0:38:19.120
Your Majesty values Noble Consort Lumière

0:38:19.120,0:38:21.790
and bestows this coral to bring luck to her pregnancy.

0:38:22.380,0:38:27.480
I think the most touching thing
is Your Majesty's thoughtfulness.

0:38:28.260,0:38:29.470
Your Majesty,

0:38:29.470,0:38:31.880
could Her Majesty be upset with me?

0:38:31.880,0:38:33.200
She's not.

0:38:33.350,0:38:36.629
As the Empress, she must be magnanimous.

0:38:38.795,0:38:40.045
Your Majesty,

0:38:40.400,0:38:42.060
His Majesty sent Mr. Su to invite you.

0:38:42.730,0:38:44.076
Your Majesty has no choice now.

0:38:44.690,0:38:46.050
I know.

0:38:46.320,0:38:48.900
The Palace of Eternal Longevity has always
wanted to plot against me.

0:38:50.070,0:38:53.520
But I have no intention to step into such a 
troublesome place.

0:38:54.160,0:38:56.070
But you have to consider His Majesty.

0:39:03.479,0:39:06.179
Her Majesty the Empress!

0:39:12.970,0:39:15.840
Peace and grace to Your Majesty.

0:39:17.180,0:39:18.640
I respectfully greet Your Majesty.

0:39:19.060,0:39:20.640
May Your Majesty have grace and peace.

0:39:21.140,0:39:22.440
Rise quickly.

0:39:22.440,0:39:23.584
Yes.

0:39:23.860,0:39:25.150
You are in poor health.

0:39:25.150,0:39:27.880
Do you blame me for making you come?

0:39:28.190,0:39:29.343
How could I?

0:39:29.494,0:39:32.806
I was feeling unwell,
so I wasn't planning on attending.

0:39:33.070,0:39:35.724
But Your Majesty has been concerned about Noble Consort  Lumière.

0:39:35.950,0:39:38.530
As husband and wife, we are of one heart.

0:39:38.719,0:39:40.620
How could I not care about her?

0:39:40.620,0:39:43.771
I'm late because I went to the repository

0:39:43.960,0:39:47.080
to find a statue of Guanyin Carrying a Baby
for Noble Consort Lumiere.

0:39:47.710,0:39:50.580
I hope that Noble Consort Lumiere
 can give birth smoothly.

0:39:51.590,0:39:52.630
Jiang Fuhai.

0:39:52.630,0:39:53.691
Yes.

0:39:54.140,0:39:55.932
I thank Your Majesty for your care.

0:39:57.060,0:40:00.480
I will place this statue of Guanyin
in my chamber and offer incense day and night.

0:40:09.690,0:40:11.349
The Empress is virtuous.

0:40:11.740,0:40:14.730
Your Majesty, may I make a bold request?

0:40:15.070,0:40:17.120
Since Her Majesty is so caring towards the harem,

0:40:17.120,0:40:22.160
I wish to dedicate my coral to her, like
"offering a borrowed flower to the Buddha"

0:40:24.120,0:40:27.330
It is admirable that Noble Consort Lumiere 
has such esteem for Her Majesty.

0:40:27.330,0:40:31.449
It's just that His Majesty gave you this coral
on account of your pregnancy.

0:40:31.789,0:40:33.449
I want for nothing.

0:40:33.880,0:40:37.120
Noble Consort Lumiere,
you should keep the coral for your own pleasure.

0:40:37.800,0:40:41.240
You must not disappoint the good
intentions of His Majesty and mine.

0:40:42.850,0:40:44.312
Your Majesty is benevolent.

0:40:44.480,0:40:46.650
Imperial Noble Consort and I are also here today

0:40:46.650,0:40:51.192
to pray for Noble Consort Lumiere's 
timely delivery of another prince.

0:40:53.860,0:40:55.662
Noble Consort Lumiere,

0:40:55.910,0:40:57.990
have the priests delivered the talismans?

0:40:58.402,0:40:59.534
They're here.

0:41:00.240,0:41:01.413
Xiao Yunzi?

0:41:02.500,0:41:03.542
Your Highness.

0:41:12.130,0:41:13.340
Your Majesty,

0:41:13.970,0:41:15.220
the priests said that

0:41:15.220,0:41:17.630
both the talismans and lucky sachets can bring auspiciousness.

0:41:18.100,0:41:19.800
They can bless the baby in my belly

0:41:19.800,0:41:21.390
with safety and health.

0:41:21.390,0:41:23.930
But I must trouble Your Majesty and my two fellow consorts

0:41:23.930,0:41:26.930
to help me place the talismans into the sachets

0:41:26.930,0:41:28.470
and hang them by my bedside.

0:41:29.610,0:41:32.000
It's as "easy as lifting our hands."

0:41:32.570,0:41:35.169
Your Majesty, Noble Consort Lumiere is pregnant.

0:41:35.650,0:41:38.070
There is a fetal god guarding her chamber.

0:41:39.200,0:41:40.593
I am unwell.

0:41:41.280,0:41:44.600
And a stranger entering her chambers 
will displease the fetal god.

0:41:44.600,0:41:46.000
That would be thoughtless of me.

0:41:46.000,0:41:47.742
Imperial Noble Consort and Noble Consort Estime

0:41:47.742,0:41:51.000
are willing to make such a small effort for my heir.

0:41:51.000,0:41:54.240
Why are you making every effort 
to shirk your responsibilities?

0:41:54.260,0:42:00.846
You possess the Phoenix Seal:
you must bring harmony to the harem.

0:42:01.680,0:42:03.970
Since Noble Consort Lumière became pregnant,

0:42:03.970,0:42:06.090
Her Majesty hasn't visited the Palace of Eternal Longevity.

0:42:06.940,0:42:10.100
Your Majesty shouldn't see yourself as a stranger.

0:42:10.480,0:42:13.480
There are no concerns with Your Majesty visiting more often.

0:42:13.860,0:42:15.850
Noble Consort Estime is right.

0:42:17.280,0:42:18.140
Yes.

